HEADWORD: Tolyl
<hw>Tol"yl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Tol</ets>uic +
<ets>-yl</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>The hydrocarbon radical,
<chform>CH3.C6H4</chform>, regarded as characteristic of certain
compounds of the aromatic series related to toluene; <as>as,
<ex>tolyl</ex> carbinol</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
